title: MemoQ 2013 R2 Project Manager version
description:
1. Download
2. Go to C_Activation in downloaded folder
3. Depend on your OS platform copy content from x86 or x64 and paste them accordingly to MemoQ installation folder "C:...KilgrayMemoQ 2013 R2x86 or x64" overwriting existing file.
4. Double click "EmulatorVersion_6852.reg" to merge value to Windows registry.
5. Enjoy!
6. Seed and if you like the software, buy it to support the company.
